'''里山镇'''是中国[[浙江省|浙江省]]西北部[[杭州市|杭州市]][[富阳区|富阳区]]下辖的一个[[镇|镇]]<ref name="陸景宇1977">{{cite book|author=陸景宇|title=新編中國地名辭典|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=iJxCAAAAYAAJ|year=1977|publisher=維新書局|access-date=2019-03-16|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630194633/https://books.google.com/books?id=iJxCAAAAYAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==历史==
1942年，侵华日军曾对里山镇进行扫荡，共焚毁民房159间<ref name="中共浙江省委党史研究室2015">{{cite book|author=中共浙江省委党史研究室|title=日军侵略浙江罪行专题集|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MnV9DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT183|date=1 July 2015|publisher=|isbn=978-7-213-06773-0|page=183|access-date=2019-03-16|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630194631/https://books.google.com/books?id=MnV9DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT183|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

